      <title>美联储按兵不动，市场需要调整：CalSTRS CIO Ailman</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-30/fed-on-hold-markets-need-to-adjust-calstrs-cio-ailman</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州教师退休金计划 (CalSTRS) 首席投资官克里斯托弗·艾尔曼 (Christopher Ailman) 表示，市场必须重新适应美联储降息预期，未来可能会出现 10%-13% 的抛售。他在“彭博市场”上发表了讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-30/fed-on-hold-markets-need-to-adjust-calstrs-cio-ailman</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 20:23:14 GMT</pubDate>
